</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="14" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,151,609]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,332,438,464]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Discussion.</emphasis>
Both specimens of this species are heavily glued to cards, making determination of the sex of the 
<typeStatus box="[151,247,475,501]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">paratype</typeStatus>
difficult. My side-view examination of the ventrally flattened abdomen indicates the 
<typeStatus box="[1207,1303,475,501]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">paratype</typeStatus>
probably is a female.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
